## Project Structure Rules

### Frontend (Groupify-frontend/)
```
src/
├── components/           # React components
│   ├── ui/              # shadcn/ui components (DO NOT manually edit)
│   ├── figma/           # Figma-generated components
│   └── *.tsx            # Screen/feature components
├── hooks/               # Custom React hooks (useFeature.ts)
├── contexts/            # React Context providers
├── lib/                 # Utilities, API client, config
├── types/               # TypeScript interfaces
└── styles/              # Global styles
```

### Backend (Groupify-backend/)
```
src/
├── routes/              # Route definitions (*Routes.js)
├── controllers/         # Request handlers (*Controller.js)
├── services/            # Business logic (*Service.js)
├── models/              # Database schemas (*.js)
├── middleware/          # Express middleware
├── validators/          # Input validation (*Validator.js)
└── utils/               # Helper functions
```

### Root Documentation (/)
```
docs/                    # ALL documentation files go here
├── HOW_IT_WORKS.md
├── QUICK_START_GUIDE.md
├── API_REFERENCE.md
└── [other guides].md
```

