## Post-Generation Summary Requirements

After generating ANY feature (frontend or backend), ALWAYS provide a summary and ALWAYS place documentation in `/docs`:

### 1. Create Documentation File
```
docs/[FEATURE_NAME]_IMPLEMENTATION.md
```

### 2. Include in Summary
- Executive summary (what was built)
- Files created/modified with descriptions
- API endpoints (if backend)
- UI components (if frontend)
- Testing instructions
- Configuration needed
- Next steps

### 3. Update Existing Documentation
- Update `docs/HOW_IT_WORKS.md` if architecture changed
- Update `docs/API_REFERENCE.md` if endpoints added
- Update `docs/QUICK_START_GUIDE.md` if new features affect getting started

